body_html:
ISSUE RESOLVED. It was a silly one.

The build process makes a bunch of git clones. As I was trying to build x64 Release mode in MSVS 2015, the 64-bit version of Git was being called and failed as I had 32-bit version installed on my system. I installed 64-bit Git and the .pb.h files were successfully generated.

Thanks for the help!
